Module jakarta.resource
Package jakarta.resource.spi

Annotation Interface AdministeredObject

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE) public @interface AdministeredObject
Designates a JavaBean as an administered object.Administered objects are specific to a messaging style or message provider.

1.6
